    "title": "Mid-Level Fleet Manager at TCI Express",
    "description": "Join the TCI Express family as a Fleet Manager in Ranchi. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout TCI Express:\nTCI Express is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with customer service teams to resolve delivery issues\n• Ensure proper handling, packaging, and labeling of goods\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Prepare MIS reports on delivery performance and SLA adherence\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n• Manage relationships with third-party logistics providers\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in Fleet Management\n• Proficiency in 3PL Management\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in Route Optimization\n• Proficiency in Reverse Logistics\n• Proficiency in Customs Clearance\n• Proficiency in TMS\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ranchi, Jharkhand, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with TCI Express!",
